| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-1041 — Recovery Inhibition (cactus)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: d129a553-0b15-52fa-95f1-e0ffda936a03"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
